data.description: This immaculate Pulte Taft plan house is located in the beautiful community of Bridgetown. Large windows allow the Florida sunshine to stream into this well-maintained 2BR/2BA + Den house. You'll be pleased by the open concept Kitchen/Dining/Living Room. The Kitchen boasts a large island with upgraded cabinets with lower cabinet pull-outs, granite countertops and recessed lighting.  You're sure to appreciate the full wall pantry. The Main Bedroom with ensuite Bathroom is split from the Guest Bedroom and Bathroom. Your guests will love their privacy. The carpet in the Bedrooms is BRAND NEW. The Den features French Doors. Enjoy relaxing on the extended lanai.  Bring your SUV to park in the 4-foot extended garage.  Bridgetown amenities include bocce, pickleball, tennis, state-of-the-art fitness center, resort-style pool, chilled lap pool, barbecue and picnic area and playground. Bridgetown is located close to RSW, restaurants and shopping. This lovely house is MOVE-IN READY!  Schedule your appointment today!
